[/asy]

solution:
Label the points as shown below: [asy]
pair A, B, C, D, E, F, G, H;
real x = 22.5;
pair A = dir(x);
pair B = dir(45+x);
pair C = dir(45*2+x);
pair D = dir(45*3+x);
pair E = dir(45*4+x);
pair F = dir(45*5+x);
